text: Annette Krier (born 10 August 1937) is a Luxembourgian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Luxembourgian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Luxembourg City
